---
title: "US62 — Manage subscription access"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as System Administrator
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>UsersScreen (detail)
  participant C as «Control»<br/>ManageSubscriptionAccess
  participant E as «Entity»<br/>Subscription · User
  A->>B: open a user's subscription detail
  B->>C: loadSubscription(userId)
  C->>E: fetchSubscription(userId)
  E-->>C: Subscription (current tier)
  C-->>B: state = AsyncData (subscription)
  A->>B: select tier, tap APPLY
  B->>C: setTier(userId, tier)
  C->>E: updateSubscriptionAccess(userId, tier)
  E-->>C: Subscription (updated tier)
  C-->>B: state = AsyncData (updated)
  B-->>A: user's access level corrected
  note over E: fetchSubscription / updateSubscriptionAccess via SupabaseGateway (RLS admin-only).<br/>manual tier assignment — payment is simulated
